snippet.title: C64 Longplay. Trollie Wallie.
snippet.description: I struggled to locate the item before the last one, hence, i took so long. A quicker longplay will be sorted soon. The game is very nostalgic for the music and bizarre looking character. I like these early games. The difficulty is high, but not stupidly so. Overall, it has an endearing charm and addictive gameplay.
